item-name: Volutz Equilibrium Series Nylon Braided Micro-USB to USB Cable - Assorted Lengths (10 Feet, 6.5 Feet, 3X 3.3 Feet), Pack of 5
item-description:
Volutz = Made by Sweden
Say hello to superior sync & charging and visionary haptics.

In Need for Hi-Speed?
Charge up to 20% faster than most OEM 2.0 USB to Micro USB cable options with speeds up-to 3A, due to extreme AWG data and power wires. Supports Quick Charge 2.0 / 3.0 and other fast USB chargers.

Reliable & Abuse Friendly
Generic aftermarket USB cables last a couple of months of use. Volutz patented craftsmanship spirit results in unrivaled durability; exceeding the lifespan of OEM USB cord you received with your device. Twist them in & out, throw them off a rooftop, even roll over these Micro-USB cords a couple of times with your office chair and they still work.

Assorted Lengths
extra-long 10ft & 6.5ft cord are perfect chargers for sofa, bed or airports.
3.3ft Cables are perfect for car chargers, office desks, or On the Go.

Perfect Snap & Click
A reassuring audible click will confirm a firm and snug connection to your device.

Craftsmanship Spirit
Our proprietary connectors will not wear out and slip out of your devices within months. The slim beveled Micro-USB plug is only 3.8mm at the tip; fitting into ANY protective case charging port. Never remove the case again to charge & sync your phone, tablet or device.

Wide Compatibility
Most Android and Windows phones, tablets and many other devices including; Samsung / Nexus / HTC / Motorola / Nokia / LG / Sony / Blackberry / PS4 Controllers / Xbox / PS Vita / Nintendo DS / GoPro / GPS devices / battery packs / Bluetooth speakers / hard drives / e-readers / printers and more.

Note: Not compatible with USB Type C devices.

item-name: iPhone Lightning Cable, Volutz MFi Certified Apple Charger Cord, Fast Charging 6ft Nylon Braided, Compatible with iPhone 11 pro Xs Max X XR 8 iPad ArmorCord Series (Moss-Green)
item-description:
DualHousing Technology
It took us 7 years to perfect our DualHousing technology. All Volutz cables are built on proprietary technology; a dual disengaged layered housing isolating bending movements and protecting the otherwise fragile connector.

Apple Ensured Compatibility
This Lightning to USB cable has passed or exceeded Apple MFi performance, safety and material standards. 

In Need for speed?
For fast charging, you need 2.4 Amps USB charger and cable with thick copper gauge (low resistance) and this is where Volutz win every time! Meet ArmorCord; our most stylish, rugged and fastest charge & sync series yet.

Dependable & Abuse-Friendly
With a confirmed 50.000+ bending tolerance, we guarantee ruggedness. Twist it in & out, throw it off a rooftop, even roll over it a couple times with your office chair and it still work. We back our promise with 2 year warranty.

Designed by haptics

  • Hybrid durable material used for a rugged anti-fry strain-relief
  • Ultra-sleek beveled tip, only 4.2mm enabling use with ANY case, including LifeProof
  • Quad woven textile fabric braid ensures the cable is tangle-free and robust
  • Ridged side grip for ergonomic haptics
  • Included cable organizer optimize cable length for various use and storage

 Compatible with past and future iOS upgrades and every device using Lightning connector including;

iPhone XR, iPhone X/XS/XS Max, iPhone 8/8 Plus, iPhone 7/7 Plus, iPhone 6/6 Plus, iPhone 6S/6S Plus

iPad Pro iPad Air 3rd gen iPad Air 2 iPad Mini 5th gen 

Apple Pencil, AirPods Charging Case, Siri Remote for Apple TV, Magic Keyboard, Magic Mouse 2, Magic Trackpad 2, EarPods with Lightning connector, BeatsX Earphones, Beats Pill+ Speaker, iPhone Lightning Dock and more.

item-name: USB C Cable/Type C to USB Fast Charging Cord [Pack of 5], Gold-Plated & Nylon Braided (10ft + 6.5ft + 2x3.3ft + 1ft) for Samsung Galaxy S8/Plus, Nexus 5X/6P, Nintendo Switch and More [Equilibrium +]
item-description:
In need for speed?
Equilibrium Series USB Type C to USB cable offer extraordinary charge and sync rates up to 3 Amperes and data transfers up-to 480 Mbps (USB 2.0).

Really Tough, dependable, and abuse-friendly
Marginalized productions and generics pollute our world. All Volutz products are developed by engineers not marketers. Twist them in and out, throw them off a rooftop, even roll over them with your office chair and they will still work.

Clever design
The USB C connector is reversible allowing you to plug in any orientation. The beveled tip is only 4.2 mm enabling use with ANY protective case; and color-coded to differentiate use among family members or devices. Including cable organizers for adjusting the perfect length and easy storage.

DualHousing™ technology
USB Cables, in general, are considered as disposables. Volutz strongly disagrees. All Volutz USB C cables are built on proprietary DualHousing technology to firmly fix connector and isolate bending movements resulting in 15x prolonged lifespan compared to standard Type-C cables.

You get
5X USB Type C Cable to Type- A (10ft + 6.6ft + 2x3.3ft + 1 ft)
Retail Box (100% environmentally degradable)
2-year Warranty
